{"data":[{"name":"91:1","price":"Güneş'e ve onun aydınlığına andolsun.","arabic":"وَٱلشَّمۡسِ وَضُحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6044,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-shamsi waḍuḥāhā ","translations":["By the sun","and its brightness","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-shamsi","waḍuḥāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,2575]]}},{"name":"91:2","price":"Onu izlediğinde Ay’a andolsun.","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا تَلَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6045,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-qamari idhā talāhā ","translations":["And the moon","when","it follows it","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-qamari","idhā","talāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,1630],[3,1630,3095]]}},{"name":"91:3","price":"Onu ortaya çıkardığında gündüze andolsun.","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا جَلَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6046,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nahāri idhā jallāhā ","translations":["And the day","when","it displays it","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nahāri","idhā","jallāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2240],[2,2240,2870],[3,2870,4345]]}},{"name":"91:4","price":"Onu bürüdüğünde geceye andolsun.","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6047,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā yaghshāhā ","translations":["And the night","when","it covers it","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","yaghshāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1750],[3,1750,3315]]}},{"name":"91:5","price":"Göğe ve onu bina edene andolsun.","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَمَا بَنَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6048,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāi wamā banāhā ","translations":["And the heaven","and (He) Who","constructed it","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāi","wamā","banāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2670],[2,2670,3340],[3,3340,4575]]}},{"name":"91:6","price":"Yeryüzüne ve onu yayıp döşeyene andolsun.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا طَحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6049,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-arḍi wamā ṭaḥāhā ","translations":["And the earth","and by (He) Who","spread it","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-arḍi","wamā","ṭaḥāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,1650],[3,1650,2935]]}},{"name":"91:7","price":"Nefse ve ona bir düzen içinde biçim verene.","arabic":"وَنَفۡسٖ وَمَا سَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6050,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"wanafsin wamā sawwāhā ","translations":["And (the) soul","and (He) Who","proportioned it","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wanafsin","wamā","sawwāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1750],[2,1750,2260],[3,2260,3835]]}},{"name":"91:8","price":"Sonra da ona günahını ve takvasını ilham etmiş olana (andolsun ki).","arabic":"فَأَلۡهَمَهَا فُجُورَهَا وَتَقۡوَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6051,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-alhamahā fujūrahā wataqwāhā ","translations":["And He inspired it","(to distinguish) its wickedness","and its righteousness","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-alhamahā","fujūrahā","wataqwāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1460],[2,1460,2740],[3,2740,4575]]}},{"name":"91:9","price":"Şüphe yok ki, nefsini temizlemiş olan felaha ermiştir.","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن زَكَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6052,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"qad aflaḥa man zakkāhā ","translations":["Indeed","he succeeds","who","purifies it","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["qad","aflaḥa","man","zakkāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1280],[3,1280,2220],[4,2220,3705]]}},{"name":"91:10","price":"Onu kötülüklere gömüp kirleten kimse de ziyana uğramıştır.","arabic":"وَقَدۡ خَابَ مَن دَسَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6053,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"waqad khāba man dassāhā ","translations":["And indeed","he fails","who","buries it","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["waqad","khāba","man","dassāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,540],[2,540,1290],[3,1290,2330],[4,2330,3835]]}},{"name":"91:11","price":"Semûd kavmi de nefislerinin azgınlığıyla (peygamberini) yalanladı.","arabic":"كَذَّبَتۡ ثَمُودُ بِطَغۡوَىٰهَآ","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6054,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"kadhabat thamūdu biṭaghwāhā ","translations":["Denied","Thamud","by their transgression","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["kadhabat","thamūdu","biṭaghwāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,1920],[3,1920,3585]]}},{"name":"91:12","price":"Hani onların en bedbaht olanı (fesat çıkarmak için) ileri atılınca.","arabic":"إِذِ ٱنۢبَعَثَ أَشۡقَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6055,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"idhi inbaʿatha ashqāhā ","translations":["When","(was) sent forth","(the) most wicked of them","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["idhi","inbaʿatha","ashqāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1970],[3,1970,3365]]}},{"name":"91:13","price":"Allah’ın Rasûlü de onlara şöyle dedi ki: \"Allah’ın devesin(i kesmek)ten ve su içmesin(i engellemek)ten sakının.\"","arabic":"فَقَالَ لَهُمۡ رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ نَاقَةَ ٱللَّهِ وَسُقۡيَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6056,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"faqāla lahum rasūlu al-lahi nāqata al-lahi wasuq'yāhā ","translations":["But said","to them","(the) Messenger","(of) Allah","(It is the) she-camel","(of) Allah","and her drink","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["faqāla","lahum","rasūlu","al-lahi","nāqata","al-lahi","wasuq'yāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1420],[3,1420,2340],[4,2340,3270],[5,3270,4070],[6,4070,5030],[7,5030,6745]]}},{"name":"91:14","price":"Fakat onlar, onu yalanladılar ve deveyi boğazladılar. Bunun üzerine Rableri, günâhlarından dolayı onları helâk etti ve kendilerini yerle bir etti.","arabic":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَعَقَرُوهَا فَدَمۡدَمَ عَلَيۡهِمۡ رَبُّهُم بِذَنۢبِهِمۡ فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6057,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"fakadhabūhu faʿaqarūhā fadamdama ʿalayhim rabbuhum bidhanbihim fasawwāhā ","translations":["But they denied him","and they hamstrung her","So destroyed","them","their Lord","for their sin","and leveled them","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["fakadhabūhu","faʿaqarūhā","fadamdama","ʿalayhim","rabbuhum","bidhanbihim","fasawwāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1480],[2,1480,2980],[3,2980,4080],[4,4080,5080],[5,5080,6790],[6,6790,8680],[7,8680,10555]]}},{"name":"91:15","price":"Allah, bunun sonucundan korkmaz!","arabic":"وَلَا يَخَافُ عُقۡبَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6058,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yakhāfu ʿuq'bāhā ","translations":["And not","He fears","its consequences","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yakhāfu","ʿuq'bāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,520],[2,520,1740],[3,1740,5365]]}}],"chapter":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams","Chapter Ash-Shams","Shams","Surah Shams","Chapter Shams","Ash Shams","Surah Ash Shams","Chapter Ash Shams","Surah 91","Chapter 91","The Sun","الشمس"],"version":{"key":"turkish_rwwad","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"tr","version":"1.0.0","last_update":1539637200,"title":"Turkish translation - Rowwad Tanslation Center","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Turkish by Rowwad Translation Center in cooperation with Islamhouse.com in 1440 H."}}